node.text: Do It Yourself. #telepathy (whenever I’m back in Vittorio Veneto I go quickly through my archive  always finding something I have forgotten and that somehow Im happy to have saved from time and dust. This for example is the cover of the first demo tape I have released with my label back in 1997. During a hardcore festival called Two Days Of Struggle I have collected all the fruit juices’s tetrapak packages  directly from the garbage cans and then spent a great amount of time opening and washing them to then finally insert the cassettes, that magically had the same dimensions of the packages. Recycling is good / Upcycling is better) (by the way, if you are near Vittorio Veneto tomorrow night my studio @coda.lunga is hosting a special event with @ninosdubrasil. Do It Yourself I was saying...)
Horse Power. #telepathy (less than a month left to visit @biennaledelyon)
Ninos Du Brasil. #telepathy (couldn’t be more excited about the last recording sessions for what will be @ninosdubrasil’s fourth album. infos will shortly follow) #ninosdubrasil #anotherkindofpop

Life Eternal. #telepathy (when we finished shooting the last @ninosdubrasil video directed by the one and only @carlosmcasas we just simply left behind at @coda.lunga the two caskets we used for it. Never remembering of them their first sight in the dark is always rather surprising). #orlock

Live In Tokyo. #telepathy @ninosdubrasil (Ninos Du Brasil’s Japan debut was a total blast. It feels good to be back here with @baloo_du_brasil so many years after the tour of our previous band: With Love).
